[
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說身毛喜豎經卷中",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0594b17_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譯經三藏朝散大夫試鴻臚卿",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0594b19_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "光梵大師賜紫沙門臣惟淨等",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0594b20_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "奉　詔譯",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0594b21_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0594b22_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所有地獄之道及地獄因，乃至有情所受報應，我悉能知，今復少以譬喻略明斯義。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0594b22_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0594b24_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如世間有大火聚，高等人量，或踰人量，其火熾盛，後當息滅，煙焰暖氣，而悉銷盡。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0594b24_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或有一人，於盛夏時炎暑之月，物景熾然，酷熱可畏，其人自遠而來，加復疲困，飢渴所逼，但隨道徑，詣火滅處，欲求憩止。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0594b26_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其傍有一明目之人，見彼炎熱極困苦者奔馳道徑而求憩止。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0594b29_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時明目人，竊作是念：『彼大火聚，高等人量，或踰人量，其火方息，非清涼地，是人往彼，或坐或臥，轉增熱惱，甚不適意，必受極苦。』",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0594c01_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "作是念時，彼人前往，果如所念，受極苦惱。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0594c04_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0594c05_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有一類人，墮地獄者，亦復如是！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0594c05_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼人若心若意，我悉能知，由其不知正道所行，身壞命終，墮於惡趣，生地獄中，甚不適意，受極苦惱，如來以淨天眼過於人眼，諦觀斯事。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0594c06_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0594c09_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故如來於地獄道及地獄因，乃至有情所受報應，而悉能知。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0594c09_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0594c11_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼畜生道及畜生因，乃至有情所受報應，我悉能知。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0594c11_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0594c12_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如世間有穢惡聚，高等人量，或踰人量，穢惡之物，周匝充滿。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0594c12_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或有一人，於盛夏時炎暑之月，物景熾然，酷熱可畏，其人自遠而來，加復疲困，飢渴所逼，但隨道徑，詣穢惡處，欲求憩止。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0594c14_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其傍有一明目之人，見彼炎熱極困苦者，奔馳道徑而求憩止。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0594c16_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時明目人，竊作是念：『彼穢惡聚，高等人量，或踰人量，是人往彼，非清涼地，轉增熱惱，甚不光澤，不可愛樂，必受極苦。』",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0594c18_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "作是念時，其人前往，或坐或臥，果如所念，甚不光澤，不可愛樂。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0594c20_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0594c22_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有一類人，墮畜生者，亦復如是！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0594c22_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼人若心若意，我悉能知，由其不知正道所行，身壞命終，墮於惡趣，生畜生中，甚不光澤，不可愛樂，復不適意，受極苦惱，如來以淨天眼過於人眼，諦觀斯事。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0594c23_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0594c26_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故如來於畜生道及畜生因，乃至有情所受報應，而悉能知。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0594c26_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0594c29_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼餓鬼道及餓鬼因，乃至有情所受報應，我悉能知。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0594c29_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595a01_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如有樹，高等人量，或踰人量，枯朽乾悴，枝葉凋墜。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595a01_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時有一人，於盛夏時炎暑之月，物景熾然，酷熱可畏，其人自遠而來，加復疲困，飢渴所逼，但隨道徑詣枯樹下欲求憩止。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595a02_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其傍有一明目之人，見彼人往枯樹之下而求憩止，竊作是念：『此人往彼，非清涼地，轉受其苦。』",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595a05_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "作是念時，其人前往，或坐或臥，果如所念，轉受其苦。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595a07_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595a08_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有一類人，墮餓鬼者，亦復如是！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595a09_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼人若心若意，我悉能知，由其不知正道所行，身壞命終，墮於惡趣，生餓鬼中，轉受其苦，如來以淨天眼過於人眼，諦觀斯事。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595a09_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595a12_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故如來於餓鬼道及餓鬼因，乃至有情所受報應，而悉能知。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595a12_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595a15_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼阿修羅道阿修羅因，乃至有情所受報應，我悉能知。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595a15_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595a16_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如有樹蟻聚其下，高等人量，或踰人量。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595a16_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或有一人，於盛夏時炎暑之月，物景熾然，酷熱可畏，其人自遠而來，加復疲困，飢渴所逼，但隨道徑，詣彼樹下，欲求憩止。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595a17_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其傍有一明目之人，見彼人往蟻樹之下而求憩止，竊作是念：『此人往彼，非安隱地，轉受其苦。』",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595a20_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "作是念時，其人前往，或坐或臥，果如所念，轉受其苦。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595a22_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595a23_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有一類人，墮阿修羅趣者，亦復如是！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595a23_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼人若心若意，我悉能知，由其不知正道所行，身壞命終，墮於惡趣阿修羅中，轉受其苦，如來以淨天眼過於人眼，諦觀斯事。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595a24_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595a27_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故如來於阿修羅道及阿修羅因，乃至有情所受報應，而悉能知。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595a27_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595b01_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所有人道及人趣因，乃至有情所受報應，我悉能知。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595b01_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595b02_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如有樹，高等人量，或踰人量，盤根莖幹，而悉廣大，然其枝葉，而不相等，或處踈隙、或處欝密，敷蔭于下，亦悉差別。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595b02_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或有一人，於盛夏時，炎暑之月物景熾然，酷熱可畏。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595b05_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其人自遠而來，加復疲困，飢渴所逼，但隨道徑，詣彼樹下，欲求憩止。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595b06_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其傍有一明目之人，見彼人往大樹之下而求憩止，竊作是念：『此人往彼大樹之下，或坐或臥，亦苦亦樂，間雜所受。』",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595b08_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "作是念時，其人前往，或坐或臥，果如所念，苦樂雜受。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595b10_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595b11_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一類有情，生人趣者，亦復如是！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595b12_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼人若心若意，我悉能知，由其不知聖所行道，身壞命終，生人趣中，苦樂雜受，如來以淨天眼過於人眼，諦觀斯事。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595b12_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595b15_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故如來於彼人道及人趣因，乃至有情所受報應，而悉能知。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595b15_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595b17_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所有天道及天趣因，乃至有情所受報應，我悉能知。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595b17_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595b18_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如有一高廣樓閣，周匝污墁，重複堅密，中無空隙，戶扉窓牖，而悉扃閉，使彼風日不能侵映。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595b18_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於其中間，敷設于座，以赤繒帛，而為茵縟，次第增累，厚十六重，又於其上，覆以白繒。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595b20_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或有一人，於盛夏時炎暑之月，物景熾然，酷熱可畏，其人自遠而來，加復疲困，飢渴所逼，隨路而進，欲登其上，以求憩止。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595b22_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其傍有一明目之人，見彼人來欲登其上而求憩止，竊作是念：『此人若或登其樓閣，窓戶蔭閉，茵縟重厚，甚可愛樂，而復適意，必受其樂。』",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595b25_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "作是念時，其人前往，登于重閣，或坐或臥，果如所念，受於快樂。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595b28_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595b29_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有一類人，生天界者亦復如是！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595c01_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼人若心若意，我悉能知，由其不知聖所行道，身壞命終，生於善趣天界之中，適悅快樂，如來以淨天眼過於人眼，諦觀斯事。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595c01_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595c04_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故如來！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595c04_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於彼天道及天趣因，乃至有情所受報應，而悉能知。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595c05_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595c07_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所有涅槃聖道及涅槃因，有情所證涅槃果法，我悉能知。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595c07_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595c08_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如世間城邑不遠，有天池沼，方面四等，其水清淨，澄湛可愛，周匝皆是菴摩羅樹、贍部之樹、頗拏娑樹、婆咩羅樹、俱嚩播泥嚩多樹、龍鬚樹等，遍覆四面，觸其水者，身支勝益。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595c08_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或有一人，於盛夏時炎暑之月，物景熾然，酷熱可畏，其人自遠而來，加復疲困，飢渴所逼，恒隨道路，詣彼池沼，欲飲其水，沐浴其身，滌除炎熱疲困之苦。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595c12_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其傍有一明目之人，見彼人來詣池沼處，竊作是念：『此人遠來，疲困所苦，若詣彼池，飲其水已，沐浴其身，息除炎熱疲困之苦，後當隨意詣樹影間，或坐或臥，隨其所欲，得安隱樂。』",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595c16_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "作是念時，彼人前往，果如所念。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595c20_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595c20_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有一類人證涅槃者，亦復如是！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595c21_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼人若心若意，我悉能知，由其履踐聖所行道，修涅槃因得涅槃果，諸漏已盡，非漏隨增，心善解脫，慧善解脫，以自神力，證如是法。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595c21_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來諦觀斯事，見彼有情，漏盡解脫，證法得樂：我生已盡，梵行已立，所作已辦，不受後有。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595c24_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595c26_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故如來！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595c26_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於涅槃道及涅槃法，乃至有情證涅槃果，而悉能知。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595c27_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595c28_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼長者子，於如是事，雖知雖見，以不信故，乃發是言：『沙門瞿曇！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595c28_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "尚無人中最上之法，況聖知見最勝所證，入於論難，彼為聲聞，宣說諸法，所求所修，以自辯才及不正智，而為所證，其所說法，豈能出要，盡苦邊際？』",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0595c29_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596a04_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由彼心言及彼所見相續謗故，速墮地獄，如墜重擔。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596a04_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又如聲聞苾芻，戒定慧學皆悉具足，少用勤力，智獲果證，不以為難，彼墮惡趣，亦復如是！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596a05_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596a08_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世有一類婆羅門者，作事火法，計為清淨，彼相謂言：『某甲某甲人，作事火法，而得清淨。』",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596a08_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596a10_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼事火法，極不清淨，非我往昔曾不修習，雖歷所修，終無勝利，以無始來，久遠世中，不出生死。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596a10_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而剎帝利、婆羅門及長者等，大族之中，隨見所行，求之少分人中上法尚不能得，況聖知見最勝所證。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596a12_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596a14_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼所計者，於其聖慧，不能了知，復不覺悟。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596a15_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由於聖慧不覺了故，何能出要盡苦邊際？",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596a15_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596a16_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若於聖慧，如實覺了，即能閉三有門，盡生死道，後不復生。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596a17_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596a19_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世有一類婆羅門者，以作福施會，計為清淨，彼相謂言：『某甲某甲人，作福施會，而得清淨。』",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596a19_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596a21_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼福施會，極不清淨，非我往昔曾不修習，雖歷所修，終無勝利，以無始來久遠世中不出生死。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596a21_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而剎帝利、婆羅門長者大族，隨見所行，多種作法，所謂：殺馬祀天、殺人祀天、殺象祀天、殺羊祀天，設法受食作無遮會。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596a23_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以眾色蓮華作清淨事；以白蓮華作清淨事；以物投火作祀天法、作帝釋天法、作月天法，及出金寶作施會等。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596a26_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是所修，求之少分人中上法尚不能得，況聖知見最勝所證。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596a28_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596b01_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼於聖慧，不能了知，復不覺悟。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596b01_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由於聖慧，不覺了故，何能出要，盡苦邊際？",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596b02_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596b02_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若於聖慧，如實覺了，即能閉三有門，盡生死道，後不復生。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596b03_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596b05_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世有一類婆羅門者，以自教中所有呪法，計為清淨，彼相謂言：『某甲某甲人，以其呪法，而得清淨。』",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596b05_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596b07_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼呪法者，極不清淨，非我往昔曾不修習，雖歷所修，終無勝利，以無始來久遠世中不出生死。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596b07_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而剎帝利、婆羅門長者大族隨見所行，求之少分，人中上法，尚不能得，況聖知見最勝所證。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596b09_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596b11_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼於聖慧，不能了知，復不覺悟。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596b12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由於聖慧，不覺了故，何能出要，盡苦邊際？",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596b12_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596b13_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若於聖慧，如實覺了，即能閉三有門，盡生死道，後不復生。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596b13_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596b16_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世有一類婆羅門者，在輪迴中，受生死身，計為清淨，彼相謂言：『某甲某甲人，在輪迴中，受生死身，而得清淨。』",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596b16_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596b18_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "輪迴生死，極不清淨，非我往昔不歷生死，以無始來久遠世中，不能出離，除五淨居天。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596b18_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596b20_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "淨居天中一生彼已，不復還來人間受生，即於彼天趣證涅槃。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596b20_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596b22_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "未出生死者，求之少分人中上法尚不能得，況聖知見最勝所證。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596b22_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596b24_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼所計者，於其聖慧，不能了知，復不覺悟。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596b24_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由於聖慧，不覺了故，何能出要，盡苦邊際？",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596b25_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596b26_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若於聖慧，如實覺了，即能閉三有門，盡生死道後不復生。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596b26_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596b28_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世有一類婆羅門者，以六趣處，計為清淨，彼相謂言：『某甲某甲人，往六趣處，而得清淨。』",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596b28_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596c01_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而彼六趣極不清淨，非我往昔曾所不歷，以無始來久遠世中，六趣輪轉，除五淨居天。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596c01_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596c03_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "淨居天中一生彼已，不復還來人間受生，即於彼天，趣證涅槃。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596c03_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596c04_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "未離諸趣者，求之少分人中上法尚不能得，況聖知見，最勝所證。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596c05_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596c06_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼所計者，於其聖慧，不能了知，復不覺悟。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596c06_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由於聖慧，不覺了故，何能出要，盡苦邊際？",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596c07_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596c08_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若於聖慧，如實覺了，即能閉三有門盡生死道，後不復生。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596c08_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596c11_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世有一類婆羅門者，以所生處，計為清淨，彼相謂言：『某甲某甲人，生於某處，而得清淨。』",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596c11_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596c13_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼所生處，極不清淨，非我往昔不歷所生，以無始來久遠世中，不出生死，除五淨居天。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596c13_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596c15_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "淨居天中一生彼已，不復還來人間受生，即於彼天趣證涅槃。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596c15_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596c16_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "未離所生者，求之少分人中上法尚不能得，況聖知見最勝所證。",
        "from": "T17n0757_002:0596c17_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
